<div class="content p-5 pl-0 md:px-0 flex flex-col justify-between">
<h3 class="md:text-lg">American Sniper killer Routh and Florida gunman not PTSD, both psychotics</h3>
<div class="category-date flex justify-between md:hidden">
<span class="category text-xxs uppercase"></span>
<span class="date text-xxs uppercase">Jan 07</span>
</div>
</div>
</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="news-box md:px-2 md:w-1/3">
<a href="https://sofrep.com/news/press-around-wonder-woman-may-gender-movie-still-war" class="outline-none">
<span class="flex justify-between md:flex-col items-stretch">
